assessment_details.task_description:
This Assignment aims to develop your:

ability to understand and analyse financial reports;

skills and knowledge to compare financial information of two (2) listed companies;

capacity to evaluate financial information and non-financial information to firstly recommend or reject, using financial information, a company's request for additional funding (loan) and
non-financial information relating to corporate governance principles.

Further details of the assignment will be provided prior to the first lecture.
